  10 Dec 2009; Daniel Westermann-Clark <dwc@pobox.com> files/shibd.initd:
  Pass -p to shibd to generate a pidfile more reliably

  10 Dec 2009; Daniel Westermann-Clark <dwc@pobox.com>
  shibboleth-2.3.1.ebuild:
  Use elibtoolize to reverse the LDFLAGS, preventing libtool from relinking
  against old, installed libraries

*shibboleth-2.3.1 (04 Dec 2009)

  04 Dec 2009; Daniel Westermann-Clark <dwc@pobox.com>
  -shibboleth-2.3.ebuild, +shibboleth-2.3.1.ebuild:
  Bump www-apache/shibboleth to 2.3.1

